00:16:30.406 --> 00:16:32.051
not in the clinical environment,

00:16:32.051 --> 00:16:34.466
they're meeting these kids not in crisis.

00:16:34.466 --> 00:16:37.143
They're meeting these
gorgeous kids being kids

00:16:37.143 --> 00:16:39.251
